---
title: Smart Turkey 'Pad Krapow' with Sautéed Cabbage and Carrots
description: Everyone's favourite Thai dish with a light twist! We've swapped the rice out for a bed of sautéed cabbage and carrots. Don't worry, it still has the same fragrant, sweet-spicy flavour!

Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's kilocalorie and carbohydrate amount.
